description: The fabulous Bilginer family is bringing delicious Mediterranean & European cuisine to the streets of San Diego. Their authentic menu includes scrumptious wraps with chicken or marinated grilled vegetables & mozzarella, fresh salads, an assortment of tasty kebabs, and garlic or feta cheese fries, which according to the locals, may just be the most fantastic fries you’ll ever try. There’s much more too and no matter your preferences, this talented team is receptive to all sorts of special requests, so be sure to invite Street Chef California to come cater your next event! This wonderful food is certainly worth sharing with all your guests.
name: Street Chef California
